Package oracle.kubernetes.operator.domain.model.oracle.kubernetes.weblogic.domain.v1

Class DomainStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.kubernetes.operator.domain.model.oracle.kubernetes.weblogic.domain.v1.DomainStatus

  • public class DomainStatus
extends Object
    DomainStatus represents information about the status of a domain. Status may trail the actual state of a system.
